description: Motos America Inc. does not have significant operations. It intends to buy and operate powersports dealerships, primarily European luxury motorcycle brands, including BMW Motorcycles, Triumph Motorcycles, and Ducati Motorcycles. Previously, it operated as an IT-solutions provider that offered a multi-dimensional e-commerce platform, which facilitates shopping, business, and trade, as well as integrates online and office transactions in a single application. The company was formerly known as Weconnect Tech International, Inc. and changed its name to Motos America Inc. in November 2021. The company was founded in 2015 and is based in Salt Lake City, Utah. As of October 26, 2021, Motos America Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Moto America, Inc.
